---
title: Grilled Ginger Shrimp on Chilled Noodle and Peanut Salad
description: This grilled and chilled supper is super on a hot and sunny day. Creamy peanut dressing coats the cooled noodles with lots of flavour. Fire up the grill for quick-cooking shrimp skewers and charred peppers!
